Subject: [PATCH v12 7/8] drm/xe: Add a shrinker for xe bos
Date: Fri,  1 Nov 2024 12:47:18 +0100
Message-ID: <20241101114719.3225-8-thomas.hellstrom@linux.intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.46.2
In-Reply-To: <20241101114719.3225-1-thomas.hellstrom@linux.intel.com>
